betterquesting:10.desc:8:
These pocket worlds seem to be inherently bound whoever enters them, it seems. I don't quite get it, but the magic I perform here feels more 'real', it makes more sense.
And what makes sense, is that if I want to become more powerful, sacrifice will be necessary.
But what type of sacrifice?
To grow, I think I will have to traverse some type of figurative nightmare, and survive it.
